text: Nu Med is an album by the Israeli electronica-world fusion trio Balkan Beat Box. == Track listing == All tracks written by Tamir Muskat/Ori Kaplan, except tracks 2, 5, 9, and 13, by Tamir Muskat/Ori Kaplan/Tomer Yosef. ==References== Category:Balkan Beat Box albums Category:2007 albums Category:JDub Records albums
title: Nu Med
